FBIS4-39610 "drsov111_a_94010" FBIS-SOV-94-111 Daily Report 8 Jun 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Deployment Possible During Grachev Visit Deployment Possible During Grachev Visit LD0806172294 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network in Russian 1400 GMT 8 Jun 94 LD0806172294 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network Russian BFN [Excerpt] Two or 3,000 Russian blue helmets in Abkhazia and more than 1,500 in the Armenian-Azeri conflict zone may be introduced by Russia in the near future. They will help the cease- fire and the disengagement of the combatant sides. This is primarily what Defense Minister Grachev will talk about. An informed source in the Georgian leadership does not rule out the possibility of the peacemaking operation in Abkhazia starting during Grachev's visit to the republic. [passage omitted]
